<blockquote>
  <p>2D representation</p>
</blockquote>

<font size="4">The secondary structure of the full-length hammerhead ribozyme with the general acid (red) and base (blue) is shown. The large arrow (baby blue) points to the scissile bond. The green line notes the tertiary interaction between the terminal loop of helix II and the internal loop in helix I. </font>
